features: Features double spinner wheels for superior maneuverability and maximum comfort.
Equipped with soft-touch top and side carry handles that are convenient when lifting a fully packed case
The telescopic handle locks into two positions to accommodate two or four wheel use
The main compartment of these bags is expandable for maximum packing flexibility. This feature is great when packing souvenirs on return journeys!
The interior includes two full packing compartments with elastic straps and a mesh panel to secure your belongings. A zippered lined pocket comes handy to store accessories or toiletries.
body.description: Weekend getaway? This carry-on size will suit perfectly. Lightweight, with dual spinner wheels providing effortless mobility over thick carpeting or the bumpiest of sidewalks; the Jessica collection makes the most stylish and durable travel companion.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 27, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful but arrived damaged
reviews.reviewText: I know I love this suitcase model because my partner has it and I’ve used it before to travel. Fits a ton, lightweight, easy to pack and the wheels are great. When I ordered this one, it arrived quickly but came considerably damaged with dents in the front side and warping to the inner build of the suitcase which also made it difficult to zip closed. Seems like the suitcase was forced into a box that was too small, I’ll have to return. Disappointed.
